data.description: Enjoy ample space for you and your family in this charming Avondale home. Admire the large stone wood-burning fireplace in the living room, a perfect spot for cozy gatherings. A second living area or formal dining room adjacent to the kitchen provides plenty of room for family gatherings. Take note of the updates, including both bathrooms with lovely subway tile and marble countertops. New windows throughout the home bring in plenty of natural light. The open kitchen boasts granite countertops and a dining area with French doors leading out to the backyard. Three generously-sized bedrooms and an oversized utility room offer flexibility and room for a home office. New wood fence and gate that provides secure parking in rear of home.
